name: CAPTURE_BRIGHTNESS_LEVEL_TYPE
description:
The brightness level of the video image captured by the local camera.Since
                    v3.3.0

parameters.CAPTURE_BRIGHTNESS_LEVEL_INVALID: -1: The SDK does not detect the brightness level of the video image. Wait a few seconds to get the brightness level from captureBrightnessLevel in the next callback.

parameters.CAPTURE_BRIGHTNESS_LEVEL_NORMAL: 0: The brightness level of the video image is normal.

parameters.CAPTURE_BRIGHTNESS_LEVEL_BRIGHT: 1: The brightness level of the video image is too bright.

parameters.CAPTURE_BRIGHTNESS_LEVEL_DARK: 2: The brightness level of the video image is too dark.
